'''Admiral Danish Fleet''' ('''ADMDANFLT''') can refer to:
* The [[English language|English]] name of '''''Søværnets Operative Kommando''''' (usually shortened to '''SOK''', translates directly to '''Operative Command of the Navy'''), the operationally supreme organisation of the [[Royal Danish Navy]].
* The [[rear admiral]] (''kontreadmiral'' in [[Danish language|Danish]]) who serves as the chief of naval operations of [[Denmark]] and commands the former organisation.

Since 2014, the organisation has been located at [[Karup Air Base]].

