'''Sinyar''' are the members of a minor ethnic minority in [[Chad]] and [[Sudan]] ([[West Darfur]]). Some of them speak [[Sinyar language|Sinyar]], a Nilo-Saharan language. They are Muslims and culturally [[Fur people|Fur]].

